videos.description: Duane Wilson gets a steal and then drives to the basket for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Wilson gets steal and lay-in for the Aggies

videos.description: Tyler Davis lobs up a pass for Robert Williams II who slams it down to extend A&M's lead.
videos.headline: Davis connects with Williams for alley-oop

videos.description: Admon Gilder hands it off to Tyler Davis under the basket and Davis elevates for the dunk.
videos.headline: Davis finishes with one-handed slam

videos.description: Robert Williams grabs the offensive rebound and Tonny Trocha-Morelos finishes it off with a  slam.
videos.headline: Aggies get second-chance dunk from Trocha-Morelos

videos.description: DJ Hogg drives to the basket and draws a foul on the lay-in for a three-point play.
videos.headline: Hogg extends Aggies' lead with nice layup

videos.description: DJ Hogg makes a second-chance 3-pointer, giving him 17 points against UT Rio Grande Valley.
videos.headline: Hogg sinks smooth 3-pointer
